) AS a5

    WHERE a0."TenantId" IS NULL
) AS a6 ON a5."Id" = a6."UserId"

) AS a7 ON a5."Id" = a7."UserId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."CreationTime", a."CreatorId", a."DeleterId", a."DeletionTime", a."EntityVersion", a."ExtraProperties", a."IsDeleted", a."LastModificationTime", a."LastModifierId", a."Name", a."NormalizedName"
    FROM "AbpTenants" AS a
    WHERE NOT (a."IsDeleted") AND a."NormalizedName" = @__normalizedName_0
    ORDER BY a."Id"
    LIMIT 1
) AS a1
LEFT JOIN "AbpTenantConnectionStrings" AS a0 ON a1."Id" = a0."TenantId"
ORDER BY a1."Id", a0."TenantId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."ConcurrencyStamp", a."CreationTime", a."CreatorId", a."DeleterId", a."DeletionTime", a."EntityVersion", a."ExtraProperties", a."IsDeleted", a."LastModificationTime", a."LastModifierId", a."Name", a."NormalizedName"

    WHERE NOT (a."IsDeleted") AND a."NormalizedName" = @__normalizedName_0

    LIMIT 1
) AS a1
LEFT JOIN "AbpTenantConnectionStrings" AS a0 ON a1."Id" = a0."TenantId"
ORDER BY a1."Id", a0."TenantId"
